quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,Kia tu nay na dekha kay tery rab nay hathi walon kay sath kia kiya
  105,2,Kia unkay maker ko beykar nai kerdia
  105,3,Aur unper parindon kay jhond kay jhond bhej diey
  105,4,Jo unhein mitti or pather ki kankariyan mar rahy thy
  105,5,Pus unhein khaye huye bhoosy ki tarah kerdiya